      "position": 4,
      "content": "Complete Two Lower Division History Courses The first course can be any UC transferable lower division history course offered on your campus. The second course must be one of the following courses listed in World History section below. One additional lower division course, History 99W &quot;The Historian&#39;s Workshop&quot;, will be required after transfer. This is a course in historical research, analysis, and writing. Students who choose the United States as their area of concentration are also encouraged to take HIST 17A & HIST 17B.",
